w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Wpmayor-450x302.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Wpmayor.png 1130w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>The latest WordPress news, hacks, and plugin reviews are covered in this blog. You can go through a good stuff written by a couple of contributors who give the content a multi-cultural touch. What is interesting here is the blog is run by a family. WP Mayor should be in your reading list especially when you are in the search of useful articles on WordPress platform. </p>\n<h3>12. <a href=\"https://www.codeinwp.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CodeinWP</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-1024x514.png\" alt=\"codeinwp\" width=\"1024\" height=\"514\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45759\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-1024x514.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-300x151.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-768x386.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-500x251.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-624x313.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-850x427.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-350x176.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp-450x226.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/codeinwp.png 1504w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>As the name shows, CodeinWP contains the best tutorials, tips, hacks, and useful tricks for taking the advantage of growing WordPress platform. It offers a well-managed collection of noteworthy articles liked by Daniel Pataki, Adelina Tuca, and Karol K. All the posts are written in a way that the readers tend to avoid missing any of them.</p>\n<h3>13. <a href=\"https://wparena.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WP Arena</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-1024x570.png\" alt=\"wparena\" width=\"1024\" height=\"570\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45767\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-1024x570.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-300x167.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-768x428.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-500x278.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-624x347.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-850x473.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-350x195.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena-450x251.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wparena.png 1349w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>WP Arena should also be included in the list of top WordPress blogs to follow. It is a rich blog that has a rich collection of plugin reviews, and comparisons of trending WordPress plugins. It also offers guides and awesome tips about famous WordPress plugins. The readers can find useful information on customization of their WordPress websites in WP Arena. </p>\n<h3>14. <a href=\"https://wpall.club/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPAll.club</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-1024x550.png\" alt=\"wpallclub\" width=\"1024\" height=\"550\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45774\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-1024x550.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-300x161.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-768x412.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-500x269.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-624x335.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-850x456.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-350x188.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub-450x242.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpallclub.png 1404w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Whether you are a WordPress developer, website owner, or a WordPress enthusiast, this blog has many things to offer. You can have tutorials, guides, and plugin reviews. You can get the best deals for purchasing WordPress accessories. You can also find hosting options for your website. WPAll.club also shows lists of best WordPress themes and plugins and update the same on a regular basis.</p>\n<h3>15. <a href=\"https://torquemag.io/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Torque</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-1024x502.png\" alt=\"Torque\" width=\"1024\" height=\"502\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45763\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-1024x502.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-300x147.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-768x376.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-500x245.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-624x306.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-850x417.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-350x172.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque-450x221.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Torque.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>How can we forget this platform while making a list of best WordPress blogs? Torque is made and managed by the guys who have developed WPEngine, a managed WordPress hosting. Torque brings the latest updates, news, and happenings in the WordPress domain. The blog has other useful categories including community, development, and business. Experts like John Stewart and Josh Pollock are among the top contributors of this blog.</p>\n<h3>16. <a href=\"https://www.wpkube.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPKube</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-1024x520.png\" alt=\"wpkube\" width=\"1024\" height=\"520\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45773\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-1024x520.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-300x152.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-768x390.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-500x254.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-624x317.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-850x431.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-350x178.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube-450x228.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpkube.png 1486w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Do you like how-to guides and detailed tutorials? If your answer is &#8216;yes&#8217;, then WPKube is a blog for you. It has a great collection of useful content written by a few WordPress enthusiasts from across the globe. The blog keeps the focus on providing actionable information to the WordPress developers. It covers almost all categories of WordPress. </p>\n<h3>17. <a href=\"https://www.wpsuperstars.net/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WP Superstars</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-1024x533.png\" alt=\"wpsuperstars\" width=\"1024\" height=\"533\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45760\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-1024x533.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-300x156.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-768x400.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-500x260.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-624x325.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-850x443.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-350x182.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars-450x234.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpsuperstars.png 1453w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Well, you may not consider it as a blog because it is more of a review site. However, WP Superstars has a great collection of WordPress tutorials and articles that are useful for both beginners and pros alike. Apart from reviews of WordPress plugins, themes, and hosting, you can get well-researched posts about WordPress in WP Superstars. </p>\n<h3>18. <a href=\"https://elementor.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Elementor</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-1024x497.png\" alt=\"elementor\" width=\"1024\" height=\"497\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45768\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-1024x497.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-300x145.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-768x372.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-500x242.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-624x303.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-850x412.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-350x170.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor-450x218.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/elementor.png 1524w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Elementor is a WordPress page builder plugin for free. But, what is more, interesting is it has a blog as well. Though it mostly includes the tips to build a WordPress website with the help of Elementor, it is useful for both site owners and WordPress enthusiasts. The Elementor blog also covers web design roundups, interviews of freelancers, and much more to remain relevant among other popular WordPress blogs.  </p>\n<h3>19. <a href=\"https://wpshout.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WPShout</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-1024x534.png\" alt=\"wpshout\" width=\"1024\" height=\"534\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45771\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-1024x534.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-300x156.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-768x400.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-500x261.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-624x325.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-850x443.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-350x182.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout-450x234.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/wpshout.png 1447w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>David Hayes and Fred Meyer run this blog very well through including awesome stuff. The blog covers Tutorials, security guidelines, and web development tips. Reading this blog on a weekly basis can give you more insights and useful recommendations on various resources.  </p>\n<h3>20. <a href=\"https://tutsplus.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Tuts+</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-1024x498.png\" alt=\"tuts+\" width=\"1024\" height=\"498\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45765\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-1024x498.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-300x146.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-768x373.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-500x243.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-624x303.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-850x413.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-350x170.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts-450x219.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/tuts.png 1545w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Tuts+ is also one of the popular WordPress blogs that are useful for beginners and professionals alike. It includes all handy stuff and updates of WordPress. We can consider it as a complete resource for the platform that covers reviews, articles, and tips about WordPress plugins and themes.</p>\n<h3>21. <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ThemeShaper</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-1024x557.png\" alt=\"Themeshaper\" width=\"1024\" height=\"557\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45762\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-1024x557.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-300x163.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-768x418.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-500x272.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-624x339.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-850x462.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-350x190.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper-450x245.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Themeshaper.png 1317w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Big WordPress enthusiasts like Ian Stewart, Daniel Robert, and Caroline Moore have made ThemeShaper WordPress blog awesome and appealing. Apart from attractive WordPress themes, the blog section contains a huge collection of news, tips and tricks, hacks, and detailed tutorials about WordPress platform. </p>\n<h3>22. <a href=\"https://colorlib.com/wp/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Colorlib</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-1024x558.png\" alt=\"colorlib\" width=\"1024\" height=\"558\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45781\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-1024x558.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-300x163.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-768x418.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-500x272.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-624x340.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-850x463.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-350x191.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib-450x245.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/colorlib.png 1382w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Colorlib is not just a list of best WordPress themes. Its blog has many things to offer if you&#8217;re a WordPress website owner. You can get useful guides on plugins, design tips and also free themes for your WordPress site.  </p>\n<h3>23. <a href=\"https://woocommerce.com/blog/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WooCommerce</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-1024x428.png\" alt=\"woocommerce\" width=\"1024\" height=\"428\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45790\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-1024x428.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-300x125.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-768x321.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-500x209.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-624x261.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-850x355.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-350x146.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce-450x188.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/woocommerce.png 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you have an eCommerce website or you want to develop one for your business, you have certainly heard the name of WooCommerce plugin. If you want to make a website based on WooCommerce, then this is a right blog for you. It includes guides, tips and tricks, and tutorials along with the latest developments in the WooCommerce domain. You will also get access to a number of downloadable plugins through this blog. </p>\n<h3>24. <a href=\"https://yoast.com/seo-blog/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Yoast SEO</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-1024x590.png\" alt=\"yoastseo\" width=\"1024\" height=\"590\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45791\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-1024x590.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-300x173.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-768x442.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-500x288.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-920x530.png 920w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-624x359.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-850x490.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-347x200.png 347w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo-450x259.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/yoastseo.png 1314w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Well, you may find this name a bit odd in this list, but it is one of the best blogs of Search Engine Optimization (SEO) tips for your WordPress website. From onsite SEO to WordPress SEO tactics, Yoast SEO has it all! What&#8217;s more, you can get tips for social media optimization.</p>\n<h3>25. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Solwin Infotech</a> Blog</h3>\n<p>We publish WordPress tips and tutorials on a regular basis on our blog. The WordPress blog section is a huge archive of best WordPress plugins, themes, tips &#038; tricks, news and in-depth tutorials for beginner to an advanced WordPress user. Our experienced WordPress developers have created excellent <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wordpress-themes/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress themes</a> and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wordpress-plugins/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">plugins</a> to improve the functionality of your existing WordPress website. <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Contact us</a> to know more about our services and readymade plugins for WordPress.</p>\n<h3>26. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">WordPress.org</a></h3>\n<p>Finally, we include the WordPress platform&#8217;s own news blog on this list. It covers core updates, enhancements, happenings, community activities, developers&#8217; views, and other stuff. It is fair to mention that if you have a WordPress website, you just cannot avoid going through this blog regularly to stay updated. </p>\n<p>Also, Carry Dils (A WordPress expert and enthusiast), SitePoint, WP Newsify, WPLift, Monster Post, etc. are other noteworthy names in the world of WordPress blogs. Though SitePoint is not restrained to WordPress, it contains rich resources for this platform. Here we come to an end of this mega list of best WordPress blog to follow in 2018 (and beyond)! You can also make your list of favorite blogs after going through all these websites. </p>\n<h4>Wrapping Up</h4>\n<p>WordPress is an ever-evolving platform. It&#8217;s developer community increases by leaps and bounds globally. In such a scenario, this comprehensive list of top WordPress blog to follow in 2018 and beyond can help you stand ahead of the curve. These blog platforms enable you to know the latest news and reviews about WordPress. We are sure that the names mentioned here will remain useful for you for years to come!</p>\n<p>With this, let us know in the comment box if we have missed any of your favorite WordPress blogs. We are eager to know your suggestions and thoughts.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-blogs-to-follow/\">25+ Best WordPress Blogs to Follow Right Now</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/wordpress-blogs-to-follow/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"How to Speed Up Your Magento 2 Website?\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/web-development/speed-up-magento-2-website/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:88:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/web-development/speed-up-magento-2-website/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sat, 06 Oct 2018 04:14:38 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:7:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Magento Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Magento 2 Performance Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Magento 2 Speed Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Magento 2 Speed Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"Speed Up Magento 2 Performance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Speed Up Magento 2 Website\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=45417\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:563:\"<p>Jim wanted to buy some groceries online and he was surfing for the best deal. He signed up to a local website and started looking for products he wanted to order. As the website was slow to load, he searched for another grocery shopping website and could place an order within a few minutes. If </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/web-development/speed-up-magento-2-website/\">How to Speed Up Your Magento 2 Website?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Mayur Dhudasia\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13721:\"<blockquote><p>Jim wanted to buy some groceries online and he was surfing for the best deal. He signed up to a local website and started looking for products he wanted to order. As the website was slow to load, he searched for another grocery shopping website and could place an order within a few minutes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/low-speed-issue.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/low-speed-issue.png\" alt=\"low speed issue\" width=\"500\" height=\"325\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-45421\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you own an eCommerce store, it is important to check the speed of the site. It matters a lot as no one would like to make a purchase from a website that is slow to load. You could be losing a lot of business with a sluggish website as nobody wants to waste a time in today’s busy world. Think about it!</p>\n<blockquote><p>A fast loading website can have a positive impact on your search rankings too.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Magento 2 is a popular eCommerce platform that is used by many web owners to create user-friendly web stores. Website owners should optimize their Magento 2 store to ensure success.</p>\n<p><strong>These five proven tips can enable you to accelerate your Magento 2 site.</strong></p>\n<p>Let’s dive in!</p>\n<h4>1. Check all The Third Party Extensions</h4>\n<p>Before you start working on optimizing Magento 2 website speed, you should check all the third party extensions that have been installed on your website. </p>\n<p>Several Magento 2 extensions are available for free, while some others are paid. Some Magento 2 extensions may not be developed for optimization and when installed, they may slow down your website. </p>\n<p>It is important to <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">check the speed of Magento 2 website</a> whenever you install any third party extension. It can be a good idea to turn off the extension and check the speed. </p>\n<p>If you feel that the website is faster after turning it off, then you can get in touch with the extension provider and discuss the same. You can ask the providers to replace it or fix the issue.</p>\n<h4>2. Server Requirement and Configuration</h4>\n<p>The server is a key factor that determines the performance of a website. If the server does not function properly, you cannot have a fast loading website.</p>\n<p>Investing in a good hosting provider becomes crucial when you have an eCommerce website so avoid choosing free or shared hosting. If you do not have a problem with the budget, you can opt for a <strong>dedicated server or VPN</strong>.</p>\n<p><strong>Magento 2.2.x technology stack requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Operating system (Linux x86-64)</li>\n<li>Memory requirement: Up to 2GB of RAM</li>\n<li>Composer (latest stable version)</li>\n<li>Web servers: Apache 2.2 or 2.4, nginx 1.x</li>\n<li>Database: MySQL 5.6, 5.7</li>\n<li>PHP: 7.0.13–7.0.x, 7.1.x</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://devdocs.magento.com/guides/v2.2/install-gde/system-requirements-tech.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://devdocs.magento.com/</a></p>\n<h4>3. Content Delivery Network</h4>\n<p>CDN is a system of distributed network services that provide web content to the users according to the geographic locations. It also helps the visitors load the web pages faster. </p>\n<p>To set up CDN, please go to:</p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\n<strong>Stores -> Configuration -> General -> Web -> Base URLs (Secure)</strong>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>After that, you can insert your HTTPS URLs to speed up your website.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_45429\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Content-Delivery-Network.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Content-Delivery-Network-1024x647.jpg\" alt=\"Content Delivery Network\" width=\"800\" height=\"500\" class=\"size-large wp-image-45429\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong>Image source:</strong> orpical.com</p></div>\n<h4>4. Optimize The Images</h4>\n<p>eCommerce websites have a lot of images and banners for attracting the attention of the target users and display the products. Images can affect the website’s performance. It is important to <strong>use compressed images</strong> for less data usage and faster page loading. </p>\n<p>For product images, you should use <strong>JPEG format</strong>. Logos on the website can be used in <strong>PNG or SVG format</strong>.</p>\n<h4>5. Enable Flat Catalog</h4>\n<p>One of the major problems with Magento is the read speed of the database. If your Magento 2 website has a lot of products, then you may face the problem of slow loading website. </p>\n<p>You can <strong>enable flat categories and products</strong> to increase the read speed of your database. It helps to reduce MySQL query complexity and improves the performance of your website. </p>\n<p><strong>How to enable flat options?</strong></p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\nGo to Stores -> <strong>&#8220;Configuration&#8221;</strong> in <strong>&#8220;Settings&#8221;</strong> Section -> <strong>&#8220;Catalog&#8221;</strong> in <strong>&#8220;General&#8221;</strong> Tab -> Section <strong>&#8220;Storefront&#8221;</strong> -> Fields <strong>“Use Flat Catalog Category”</strong> and <strong>“Use Flat Catalog Product”</strong> change to <strong>“Yes”</strong>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h4>6. MySQL Configuration Optimization</h4>\n<p>These are some little tips to optimize via MySQL configuration.</p>\n<p>MySQL has its own <strong>“query cache”</strong> that it uses in Magento to help generate dynamic pages and content while improving performance. These are some recommended settings for your my.cnf file.</p>\n<p><strong>You can try this:</strong></p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\n<li>query_cache_type = 1</li>\n<li>query_cache_size = 32M</li>\n<li>query_cache_limit= 2M</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>At last, This is a suggested setting for php.ini.</p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\n<li>php_value memory_limit 128M</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h4>7. Utilize Caching</h4>\n<p>Magento comes with a built-in caching module. Make sure all Cache Types are enabled by navigating to <strong>“System”</strong> → <strong>“Cache Management”</strong>.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-1024x751.png\" alt=\"Utilize Caching\" width=\"1024\" height=\"751\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45436\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-1024x751.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-300x220.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-768x564.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-500x367.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-624x458.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-850x624.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-273x200.png 273w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching-450x330.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Utilize-Caching.png 1424w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<h4>8. Change To The Production Mode</h4>\n<p>You should run Magento in production mode once it is deployed to a production server. Production mode provides the highest performance in Magento 2.</p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\n<li>php bin/magento deploy:mode:set production</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>The most important aspect of this mode is that errors are logged to the file system and are never displayed to the user.</p>\n<p><strong>In this mode,</strong> static view files are not created on the fly when they are requested; instead, they have to be deployed to the pub/static directory using the command-line tool. The generated pages will contain direct links to the deployed page resources.</p>\n<h4>9. Enable JS &#038; CSS optimization</h4>\n<p>CSS and JS file help your frontend look better. However, they are one of the core factors that slow down your site speed. Luckily you can minimize influence in Magento 2 by enabling JS &#038; CSS optimization</p>\n<p><strong>To enable JS &#038; CSS optimization:</strong></p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\nGo to “Stores” -> <strong>“Configuration”</strong>. In <strong>“Advanced”</strong> Tab -> <strong>“Developer”</strong> and in that click on the <strong>“JavaScript Settings”</strong> (Fields “Enable Javascript Bundling”, “Merge JavaScript Files”, “Minify JavaScript Files” change to “Yes”)\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-1024x239.png\" alt=\"JavaScript Settings\" width=\"1024\" height=\"239\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45441\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-1024x239.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-300x70.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-768x179.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-500x117.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-624x145.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-850x198.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-350x82.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings-450x105.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/JavaScript-Settings.png 1064w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<p>And on the same page, click on <strong>“CSS Settings”</strong> (Fields “Merge CSS Files“, “Minify CSS Files“ change to “Yes”)</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-1024x194.png\" alt=\"CSS Settings\" width=\"1024\" height=\"194\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-45442\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-1024x194.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-300x57.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-768x145.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-500x95.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-624x118.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-850x161.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-350x66.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings-450x85.png 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CSS-Settings.png 1074w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></a></p>\n<h4>10. Clean the Log Files</h4>\n<p>While optimizing the Magento database, you can also check your Magento project’s var/log directory. Sometimes it has <strong>around 200MB size</strong> so it is time for cleaning.</p>\n<p>Please take a backup first of that directory in case of rollback.</p>\n<p>After it, please go to your Magento project’s var/log directory and run below command,</p>\n<div class=\'configuration-optimization-query\'>\n<ul class=\'configuration-optimization-query-box\'>\nrm -rf *\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><strong>NOTE:</strong> Make sure that when you run the below command, you must double check that you are in your Magento project’s var/log directory.</p>\n<h4>11. Magento Updates</h4>\n<p>Magento team constantly works on improvements of performance. You should not miss out any updates and ensure that your eCommerce store is upgraded as per the <a href=\"https://magento.com/tech-resources/download\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">latest version of Magento 2</a>. You can look for expert Magento web development company to help you update your website.</p>\n<h4>Wrap Up</h4>\n<p>There can be several reasons why your Magento website is slow. It is important to identify the reasons and check all the factors to ensure the high speed of your eCommerce website. If you do not know how to check the above-mentioned points for your website, you can look for expert Magento developers to help you. Hire the best <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 web development company</a> to make your website fast loading. </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/web-development/speed-up-magento-2-website/\">How to Speed Up Your Magento 2 Website?</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/web-development/speed-up-magento-2-website/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"50+ Best Rated Multipurpose WordPress Themes From ThemeForest\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:85:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/best-multipurpose-themes-for-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/best-multipurpose-themes-for-wordpress/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 01 Oct 2018 09:32:01 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:8:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"Best Multipurpose Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:21:\"Best WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Best WordPress Themes 2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:29:\"Multipurpose WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:34:\"Multipurpose WordPress Themes 2018\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:24:\"Premium WordPress Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WP Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=32244\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:614:\"<p>Multipurpose themes are part of themes rumors because of which, many WordPress users care to stay away from. Why? It&#8217;s probably because of the famous quote “jack of all trades, master of none”. Many people falsely believe that just because a theme that has and tries to do everything, it is unable to do any </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/best-multipurpose-themes-for-wordpress/\">50+ Best Rated Multipurpose WordPress Themes From ThemeForest</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:117231:\"<p>Multipurpose themes are part of themes rumors because of which, many WordPress users care to stay away from. Why? It&#8217;s probably because of the famous quote “<strong>jack of all trades, master of none</strong>”. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Many people falsely believe that just because a theme that has and tries to do everything, it is unable to do any specific thing well.</p></blockquote>\n<p>The above assumption is just simply wrong. </p>\n<p>It is true that some of the multipurpose themes in the market are poorly coded and can&#8217;t do the job right. But, we are also aware of the fact that there are really excellent multipurpose themes available that fit wonderfully for almost all types of websites. The concept behind creating a multipurpose WordPress theme is to generate a single website layout that can go well to any types of company, organization, brand or association. </p>\n<p>These templates make it possible for anyone to make any type of website that one can imagine. Whether its publishing personal blog, portfolio, or an e-commerce site, it would be perfect for anything.</p>\n<p>So, in this article, we are going to highlight the <strong>50+ superior premium multipurpose themes</strong> that are highly tested by us to let you decide with only the best ones.</p>\n<h4>1. X Theme</h4>\n<p>X Theme is an amazingly flexible and powerful WordPress theme by Themeco with over 150,000+ sales and 4.75 out of 5 rating. This theme comes up with unique designs called stacks (majorly 4), all majorly built into just one theme. X comes with many awesome premium plugins and with which, X theme is perfectly compatible with. There are many rich features in this theme such as Navigation options, custom page, total WooCommerce integration, Page builder, shortcodes, mega menu, lightbox and so on.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme.png\" alt=\"X The Theme\" width=\"1562\" height=\"710\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32274\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme.png 1562w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-300x136.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-768x349.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-1024x465.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-500x227.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-624x284.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-850x386.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/X-The-Theme-350x159.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1562px) 100vw, 1562px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/x-the-theme/5871901?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>2. Avada</h4>\n<p>Avada is one of the best themes on ThemeForest till date, and it is a multipurpose theme. It has more than 350,000 sales and Avada is an extremely super multi-purpose WordPress theme with a perfect and fully responsive design. It has many rich plugins and features and it is mostly used for business, portfolio, corporate, product, or blog websites.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme.png\" alt=\"Avada - WP Theme\" width=\"1298\" height=\"714\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32276\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme.png 1298w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-300x165.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-768x422.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-1024x563.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-500x275.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-624x343.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-850x468.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Avada-–-WP-Theme-350x193.png 350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1298px) 100vw, 1298px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/avada-responsive-multipurpose-theme/2833226?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>3. BeTheme</h4>\n<p>This is also one another name you would&#8217;ve heard or read many times. BeTheme is another amazing multi-purpose WordPress with over 83000+ sale and 4.80 out 5 rating. This theme is just more than just a theme. It has various pre-built websites (currently 280+) so that you can easily import and of the demo website with just 1 click. BeTheme even comes with many premium plugins such as Revolution Slider and impressive features like Advanced options. Drag and Drop builder, 7 header version and layout generator, mega menu and much more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme.png\" alt=\"Be Theme\" width=\"1583\" height=\"752\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32277\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme.png 1583w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-300x143.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-768x365.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-1024x486.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-500x238.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-624x296.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-850x404.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-350x166.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Be-Theme-450x214.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1583px) 100vw, 1583px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/betheme-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/7758048?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>4. TheGem</h4>\n<p>Similar to all other themes in this list, TheGem also aims to be a theme that does all. For the most of the part, It has 12000+ sales with 4.76 out of 5-star rating. TheGem gives more than 150 demo pages that can be imported with just a click. It also offers plenty of customization with Visual Composer plugin, 2500+ font icons, one-pager and full screen, multiple mega menu and child themes support and many much more. TheGem has an international customer focus, and thus it is offering support in English, Russian, and German.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem.png\" alt=\"Meta Splash - TheGem\" width=\"1575\" height=\"621\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32278\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem.png 1575w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-300x118.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-768x303.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-1024x404.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-500x197.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-624x246.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-850x335.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-350x138.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Meta-Splash-–-TheGem-450x177.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1575px) 100vw, 1575px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/thegem-creative-multipurpose-highperformance-wordpress-theme/16061685?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>5. Mist</h4>\n<p>If you are looking for any creative or differently quirky WordPress theme that gives the ability to improve every aspect of your website, you can stop here on Mist. It has 1200+ sales with 4.70 out of 5-star rating. Mist has much stuff to offer. It allows you to customize and build every page the way you want, and also has many pre-designed templates and layouts to make it on the go! The Page builder has more than 130 options, Visual composer enabled, fully responsive, and any mobile friendly adaption. It comes many premium and rich plugins with it like, Contact form 7, Gravity form, Bootstrap forms, visual composer, events calendar and more. </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Mist-–-Best-Multipurpose-Responsive-Theme.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Mist-–-\nBest-Multipurpose-Responsive-Theme.png\" alt=\"Mist - Best Multipurpose Responsive Theme\" width=\"1299\" height=\"716\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32279\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/mist-advanced-multiconcept-theme/12023626?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>6. Infinite</h4>\n<p>Inifinite is eligible enough to be listed on this list of Great themes. This theme is a multipurpose WordPress theme that has around 4500+ sales and 4.80 out of 5-star rating. It comes with awesome 20+ demos with a one-click install. Compatibility with WooCommerce makes it more powerful and gives customers an amazing E-commerce experience. Infinite offers infinite customization of pages and is 100% responsive. Provides astonishing mega menu, drag and drop page builder, and several other premium sliders. Can customize unlimited sidebars, color skins, footers, multiple headers, and backgrounds too. Infinite is infinitely perfect!</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Infinite-Multi-Purpose-Responsive-WordPress-Theme.png\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/Infinite-Multi-Purpose-Responsive-WordPress-Theme.png\" alt=\"Infinite WordPress Theme\" width=\"156