ds/2018/09/Cuber-Responsive-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-350x159.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Cuber-Responsive-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-450x205.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1343px) 100vw, 1343px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/cuber-responsive-multipurpose-wordpress-theme/22017070?ref=solwin\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/download-button.png\" alt=\"download button\" width=\"240\" height=\"46\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-32302\" /></a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<h4>52. XTRA </h4>\n<p>Xtra is an excellent WordPress theme with more than 200 pre-made templates. This is very fast and SEO optimized WordPress theme. Editing website is just at your fingertip with drag and drop feature that you get from this theme. It is bundled with many exciting features like RTL support, WPML ready, mega menu etc. This theme is also integrated with WP Bakery and Revolution Slider Plugins.</p>\n<p> <a href=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme.jpg\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme.jpg\" alt=\"XTRA - Multipurpose WordPress Theme\" width=\"1343\" height=\"611\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-45186\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme.jpg 1343w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-300x136.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-768x349.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-1024x466.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/XTRA-Multipurpose-WordPress-Theme-500x227.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/20