{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"Content Marketing Best Practices\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Content Marketing Guide\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Content Marketing Strategy\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Content Marketing Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=42128\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:621:\"<p>Whenever it comes to digital marketing, we all have heard that content is king. It will be like over saying but it is a fact that content marketing strategy has been stayed for so long. Yeah, content marketing holds the priority in the world of digital marketing. As it holds the power to inspire and </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/content-marketing-strategy-for-business/\">Why Your Business Needs Content Marketing Strategy? (Beginner&#8217;s Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Anupam Bhagat\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16660:\"<p>Whenever it comes to digital marketing, we all have heard that content is king. It will be like over saying but it is a fact that <strong>content marketing strategy</strong> has been stayed for so long.</p>\n<p>Yeah, content marketing holds the priority in the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/top-digital-marketing-trends/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">world of digital marketing</a>. As it holds the power to inspire and convert the potential customer in near future. Content marketing also showcases your authority.</p>\n<p>Content marketing is not just writing a few blogs-articles or add more pages to your website. It is really complex and believes me, it is a lot more than what you think.</p>\n<p>It has a very broad spectrum. Each website is unique with different business goals. Hence content strategies also differ. </p>\n<h4>Let’s explore what is exactly content marketing?</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-1024x487.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"487\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-42133\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-1024x487.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-300x143.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-768x366.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-500x238.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-624x297.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-850x405.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-350x167.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-450x214.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>Creating and distributing valuable information consistently to target your niche audience is content marketing. It is a strategic sure shot approach to reach your targeted audience but it is quite a slow process. </p>\n<p>In recent years, it has been found that many top-notch brands have focused on generating content as much as possible. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Content Gives Compounding Rates of Return.</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI-.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"617\" height=\"305\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-42134\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI-.png 617w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI--300x148.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI--500x247.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI--350x173.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-marketing-ROI--450x222.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 617px) 100vw, 617px\" /></p>\n<p>In one of the articles in <strong>Forbes by Jayson Demers</strong>, he mentioned, “As your investment earns interest, your principal grows and you earn more interest with each subsequent round of compounding. Content works much the same way since it’s more or less “permanent.” If you publish twice a week, you’ll have 110 pieces the first year, so the first year you’ll produce 110 pieces and get 110 pieces’ worth of results. The second year, you’ll produce 110 pieces and see 220 pieces’ worth of results.”</p>\n<blockquote><p>Every article or content you write is just like a strong real estate property that will stay forever.</p></blockquote>\n<div id=\"attachment_42140\" style=\"width: 810px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-.jpg\" alt=\"Content Marketing\" width=\"800\" height=\"418\" class=\"size-full wp-image-42140\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-.jpg 800w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--300x157.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--768x401.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--500x261.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--624x326.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--350x183.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing--450x235.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Content Marketing</p></div>\n\n<p>DeMers’ theories are that content gives a compounding rate of return. This compounding rate of return means your content is always available to you and can help to drive sales. If you create evergreen content in addition to news posts and trending topic-led pieces, you’ll also have a stockpile of information that you can turn to time and time again, whenever you need interesting, useful pieces for emails, slideshows, social posts, and other marketing activities.</p>\n<blockquote><p>Content on your website will help to build faith in your brand.</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"638\" height=\"359\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-42135\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust.jpg 638w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust-300x169.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust-500x281.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust-624x351.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust-350x197.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Content-Marketing-and-Brand-trust-450x253.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 638px) 100vw, 638px\" /></p>\n<p>You can no more stuff the keywords in the webpage or blog to rank well. You really need a content which should be <strong>highly shareable, entertaining, and useful</strong> enough to engage your visitors. If you have written a valuable piece, your customer will believe you. </p>\n<h4>Accomplish both targets:</h4>\n<p>Content build the value of your webpage or landing pages. You have to target humans as well as search engines when you write a piece. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670.jpg\" alt=\"content marketing for small businesses\" width=\"700\" height=\"453\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44986\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670.jpg 700w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670-300x194.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670-500x324.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670-624x404.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670-309x200.jpg 309w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/content-marketing-for-small-businesses-e1537772141670-450x291.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" /></p>\n<h4>Interlinking:</h4>\n<p>Interlinking becomes easy and fruitful when you have more content on your blog as well as website. Passing link juice to the lesser ranking page becomes very easy with content strategies.<br />\n<strong>Content can be in any form:</strong><br />\n1. Video<br />\n2. Audio<br />\n3. Infographics<br />\n4. Textual articles</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_42331\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-1024x700.jpg\" alt=\"Internal Content Linking-map\" width=\"1024\" height=\"700\" class=\"size-large wp-image-42331\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-1024x700.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-300x205.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-768x525.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-500x342.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-624x427.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-850x581.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-292x200.jpg 292w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1-450x308.jpg 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Internal-Content-Linking-map-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: Techiexpert.com</p></div>\n<p>What is more important is that your content should be convincing enough. Let your potential customers reach your content and they contact you, this type of conversion is more genuine. </p>\n<p>Most of the companies are still not doing the right content management; hence you can start doing it. If you have just started your content strategy, I have shared some tips here that you will need to consider in this year. </p>\n<h3>2018 Content Marketing Strategies to Follow:</h3>\n<p>With digitalization, constantly growing brands and companies have more prospects of reaching the potential customer base. It is not a short-term strategy, but definitely a beneficial long-term one. Do not miss to leverage the best of content marketing. Here are some tips mentioned which should be your business goals in 2018.</p>\n<h4>Mobile content:</h4>\n<p> It will not be a surprising thing to consider mobile marketing as the priority in upcoming years. Smartphones have already covered the most share of internet browsing today. </p>\n<p>You should consider delivering <strong>quality mobile-optimized content</strong> to your customers. The hottest mobile app like <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/solwininfotech/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Instagram</a> is strictly focusing on the mobile channel only.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"650\" height=\"311\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-42142\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile.jpg 650w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile-300x144.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile-500x239.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile-624x299.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile-350x167.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/content-marketing-mobile-450x215.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 650px) 100vw, 650px\" /></p>\n<h4>Native advertising:</h4>\n<p> Gone are the days when customers were attracted towards the traditional banner ads, now businesses will need to involve into more real content marketing efforts and appeal to their customers in a human way.  </p>\n<p>Native ads are generally served with the specific goal to promote your business through a platform that correlates the content of the media through which you are publishing. If you don’t know <a href=\"https://www.sharethrough.com/nativeadvertising/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">what native advertising is</a>, it is a right time to get into it. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-1024x537.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"537\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-42144\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-1024x537.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-300x157.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-768x403.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-500x262.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-624x327.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-850x446.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-350x184.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/Native-Advertizing-450x236.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<h4>Influencer marketing:</h4>\n<p> According to my experience of SEO, <strong>most consumers believe other consumers</strong> who shops online just like themselves. The audience will believe the recommendations of another consumer if your piece of content is shared by their friend. It adds an incredible credit to the content and thus results in conversions.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-1024x536.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"536\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-42146\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-1024x536.jpg 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-300x157.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-768x402.jpg 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-500x262.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-624x327.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-850x445.jpg 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-350x183.jpg 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing-450x236.jpg 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/influencer-marketing.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>Most of them check reviews before making any online purchase. It is for sure that if you back your brand with strong genuine reviews including a local personality, celebrity or any influential person, your business outputs will increase in folds.  </p>\n<h4>Marketing automation:</h4>\n<p>Content Marketing is a very gradual and time-consuming process. You can use some <a href=\"https://www.entrepreneur.com/article/286039\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">content automation system</a> for certain actions and tasks to save time and improve the efficiency of your overall content marketing efforts. If you are unaware of this content automation, feel free to contact us.</p>\n<p>Follow the above strategies to get the right kind of audience for your business. </p>\n<h4>Conclusion:</h4>\n<p>Any form of content whether it is a news, information or trend statistics it will never decay. Properly formed keyword enriched content will reap the benefits of Google Search Ranking. Semantic, long-tail topics overtook keyword-focused strategy with content marketing.</p>\n<p>With implementing content strategy sooner, you will start seeing the benefits in near future. In my next article, I am going to show you how you built a proper SEO marketing content. If you are very busy to do content marketing on your own, let <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Solwin Infotech</a> do it for you. </p>\n<p>So stay tuned to our posts and do not forget to share your feedback in the comments section.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/content-marketing-strategy-for-business/\">Why Your Business Needs Content Marketing Strategy? (Beginner&#8217;s Guide)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:99:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/digital-marketing/content-marketing-strategy-for-business/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"20+ Most Effective Magneto 2 SEO Tips to Enhance Visibility of Your Online Store\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 12 Sep 2018 13:57:39 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:10:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Magento Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:26:\"Search Engine Optimization\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"magento\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20:\"Magento 2 SEO Agency\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Magento 2 SEO Services\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Magento 2 SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:18:\"Magento 2 Site SEO\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Magneto SEO Tips\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:8;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3:\"seo\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"SEO Tips Magento\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=44460\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:641:\"<p>Magento is one of the most preferred open-source platforms to build a robust eCommerce store. We can have an idea of its growing popularity through the fact that over 250,000 merchants rely on this platform to run their eCommerce business. After the advent of revolutionary Magento 2 version, this number increases significantly as Indian, Australian, </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/\">20+ Most Effective Magneto 2 SEO Tips to Enhance Visibility of Your Online Store</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30518:\"<p>Magento is one of the most preferred open-source platforms to build a robust eCommerce store. </p>\n<p>We can have an idea of its growing popularity through the fact that over <strong>250,000 merchants</strong> rely on this platform to run their eCommerce business. </p>\n<p>After the advent of revolutionary Magento 2 version, this number increases significantly as Indian, Australian, and Canadian eCommerce store owners have also started using this system.</p>\n<h4>Why retailers use Magento?</h4>\n<p>The global top brands including Coca-Cola, Burger King, and Zumiez count on the Magento platform. <strong>Here are a few reasons why retailers use Magento for building their eCommerce website:</strong> </p>\n<li>It can handle millions of orders at once with 99.999% uptime.</li>\n<li>It is one of the most flexible platforms that gives the online shop a unique experience.</li>\n<li>It has hundreds of thousands of high-quality integration and customized extensions.</li>\n<li>It offers 24/7 support worldwide.</li>\n<p><br />\nAll these benefits attract the vendors to build their online stores in Magento. Apart from these benefits, the <b>Magento 2 platform</b> is capable of enhancing the website’s visibility through its excellent SEO support. However, SEO remains challenging for the store owners in their Magento 2 store. </p>\n<p>Here we give some of the <b>highly effective Magento 2 SEO tips</b> to enable you to optimize your site for top search engines like Google and Bing.</p>\n<h4>1. Check and increase page loading speed</h4>\n<p>Your website speed is one of the most powerful factors to affect your SEO efforts.</p>\n<p>Though Magento 2 offers faster page load speed than its predecessor Magento 1, you should <a href=\"https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">check and increase the speed</a> even more. The faster speed not only helps you get a higher online visibility but also enables you to provide a pleasant user experience.  </p>\n<p class=\"text-center\"><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/13jOMJhKISE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p class=\"text-center\">Source: Neilpatel.com</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Install defer JavaScript extension. It allows HTML and CSS to be loaded before JS to increase the loading speed of your website. You can also <strong>merge CSS and JS files and optimize images</strong> to increase the site speed. Experienced <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/hire-magento-developer/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento developers</a> can easily perform these tasks.</p>\n<h4>2. Make your website mobile-friendly</h4>\n<p>In the age of mCommerce, your eCommerce website should be mobile-friendly or responsive. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/mobile-friendly-website.png\" alt=\"mobile friendly website\" width=\"400\" height=\"315\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44471\" /></p>\n<p>Even Google also prefers such websites in giving the higher ranks. Magento 2 framework enables the developers to build a responsive website, which runs seamlessly across various devices.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Apart from being responsive, your eCommerce store should support <a href=\"https://www.ampproject.org/learn/overview/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google AMP</a> (Accelerated Mobile Pages). The AMP is four times faster than normal mobile-friendly pages. Such pages can also support the SEO campaigns in the future. </p>\n<p>As <strong>Magento 2 does not support the AMP version</strong> of your eCommerce store, it is better to keep your website’s structure simple.</p>\n<h4>3. Make the navigation easy and simple</h4>\n<p>Any eCommerce website needs a simple and easy-to-use navigation. It can help the visitors or customers browse what they want with ease.</p>\n<p>While working on navigation, you need to remain careful in designing filters because the Googlebot can waste your bandwidth while crawling in and out of them. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Integration of AJAX (Asynchronous JavaScript And XML) framework can make your Magento 2 store’s navigation SEO-friendly. However, the Magento 2 platform does not support this feature, so you need to try a custom Magento extension. Also, a third-party extension like <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/previous-next-product-navigation-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Previous Next Product Navigation</a> and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-category-slider-magento-2-extension/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Advanced Category Slider</a> are a few excellent third-party extensions for your Magento 2 store, which can make the navigation and product search easier for your customers.</p>\n<h4>4. Keep relevant URLs</h4>\n<p>How about keeping the following URL for your product webpage?</p>\n<p><b>website.com/category-sub-category/year of website building/</b></p>\n<p>Do you find it relevant? Now, let’s go through the following URL:</p>\n<p><b>website.com/category-sub-category/product-name/</b></p>\n<p>You can certainly consider the above URL ideal for the product page. If you give relevant titles to the URLs, Google will find out the theme of your page. Automatically such a page becomes optimized for the search engines.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Do not add any irrelevant and unnecessary information in the URL. The <strong>URL is like an ID</strong> through which your webpage is known for the search engines. It is advisable to follow the ideal structure while making the URLs. </p>\n<h4>5. Set up Google Search Console and Analytics</h4>\n<p>Well, this is the first and foremost requirement to start SEO for your Magento 2 website. Google Search Console or <a href=\"https://www.google.com/webmasters/tools/home\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Webmaster Tools</a> can enable you to track and manage your eCommerce site’s performance, whereas <a href=\"https://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Analytics</a> can help you track the web traffic on your site.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44702\" style=\"width: 1210px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc.png\" alt=\"Google Search Console And Analytics\" width=\"1200\" height=\"600\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44702\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc.png 1200w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-300x150.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-768x384.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-1024x512.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-500x250.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-624x312.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-850x425.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-350x175.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/ga-gsc-450x225.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: Serps.com</p></div>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Here you should take care of domain and subdomain. You should set up the domain in the Google Search Console. The SERPs (Search Engine Ranking Pages) will show this domain and Google will consider it for the ranking. A third-party extension <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/google-custom-search-integration-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Custom Search Integration</a> can also enhance the search functionality of your Magento 2 store.</p>\n<h4>6. Make your website more secure</h4>\n<p>Many website owners argue that HTTP makes the website secure and there is no need of HTTPS.</p>\n<p>It is true that HTTPS is an advanced version of HTTP and provides more security, but when it comes to the eCommerce website, you should opt for HTTPS.</p>\n<p>The reason is simple. Hundreds of thousands of customers visit your website on a weekly or monthly basis. It makes your website a soft target for hackers, and the valuable data of your customers can be at risk. In this situation, HTTPS is more preferable for an online shop.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44479\" style=\"width: 647px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https.jpg\" alt=\"http-vs-https\" width=\"637\" height=\"400\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44479\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https.jpg 637w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https-300x188.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https-500x314.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https-624x392.jpg 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https-319x200.jpg 319w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/http-vs-https-450x283.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 637px) 100vw, 637px\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: comodosslstore.com</p></div>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> In the year 2014, Google has announced that it will prefer HTTPS as compared to HTTP for ranking. Therefore, you should opt for HTTPS for your store.</p>\n<h4>7. Use Robots txt file and XML Sitemap</h4>\n<p>When Magento 2 is installed, the eCommerce web developers place the robots.txt file in the root. The search engine crawlers read this robots file and indexing your website accordingly. In a way, the <strong>Magento 2 Robots.txt file plays a significant role</strong> in optimizing your website. </p>\n<p>Also, you should generate a Magento 2 XML sitemap. You have two default options available in Magento 2 for XML sitemap. They are frequency setting and priority for the updates of product and category pages. </p>\n<p>You can readily generate a basic XML sitemap and submit It to Google Search Console. It helps the search bot to index your website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap.png\" alt=\"xml-sitemap\" width=\"1328\" height=\"443\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44485\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap.png 1328w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-300x100.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-768x256.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-1024x342.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-500x167.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-624x208.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-850x284.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-350x117.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/xml-sitemap-450x150.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1328px) 100vw, 1328px\" /> </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> If you have an eCommerce store with a wide range of products, it is better to upgrade the default XML sitemap. It provides better crawling. However, it is also necessary to divide the sitemap and exclude a few private links to avoid any misuse by hackers. </p>\n<h4>8. Improve indexing by generating HTML Sitemap</h4>\n<p>Do you know that if your website has no HTML sitemap, you miss the chance of indexing it more carefully by Google?</p>\n<blockquote><p>It is a plain fact that HTML sitemap is also as important as the XML sitemap.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Apart from indexing, the HTML sitemap also helps the visitors search for products on your website. But, here there is a small problem. Magento supports the HTML sitemap, but Magento 2 is currently not supporting it. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> You can opt for a third-party extension for generating HTML sitemap in your Magento 2 store.</p>\n<h4>9.  Use rich snippets</h4>\n<p>It is fair to mention that the more information about your product and store on the SERPs (Search Engine Ranking Pages) can result in a higher CTR (Click Through Rate). You can serve this purpose by using the rich snippets. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets.png\" alt=\"rich snippets\" width=\"689\" height=\"293\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44496\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets.png 689w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets-300x128.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets-500x213.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets-624x265.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets-350x149.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/rich-snippets-450x191.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 689px) 100vw, 689px\" /></p>\n<p>The rich snippets are nothing but a type of structured data markups that helps Google understand the website’s content. Rich snippets also enable the search engine to show special features on the search result pages like product rating and review, social links, logo, and address. Such business-related information can enhance the trustworthiness.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Magento 2 platform only supports rating and review as rich snippets. However, you can improve the default Magento 2 rich snippets by using a third-party extension.</p>\n<h4>10. Integrate Open Graph and Twitter Cards</h4>\n<p>It is easy to show the preview of title, meta description, and even images along with URL if your Magento 2 store support tags for social networks. <a href=\"http://ogp.me/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Open Graph</a> and <a href=\"https://developer.twitter.com/en/docs/tweets/optimize-with-cards/overview/abouts-cards.html\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter Cards</a> tags enable you to serve this objective for Facebook and Twitter respectively.</p>\n<p>These tags enable your users or visitors to share a web page URL along with a title, description, etc. However, Magento 2 does not support both these tags currently.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Magento web developers can help you implement these tags on your eCommerce website. You can also opt for purchasing a third-party extension for this useful functionality.  </p>\n<p><strong>Now we will go through some effective On-page Magento 2 SEO tips that can boost your SEO efforts and improve the ranking of your website.</strong></p>\n<h4>11. Avoid Duplicate and Similar Content</h4>\n<p>For a moment, just put your legs in the visitor’s shoes. </p>\n<p>How do you feel when you find the same shirt in the different sheds (like green, blue, and red) with the same content and the different URLs? Even crawlers or search bots also punish different URLs with the same content. As a result, your online reputation decreases over the period.</p>\n<p>Here, you can take a help from a canonical tag. It enables you to tell Google which is the main URL to assign the proper search value to other pages with the similar content. Canonical URLs are highly useful for the Magento 2 store because you show many similar products in the same category. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag.png\" alt=\"canonical tag\" width=\"620\" height=\"450\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44711\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag.png 620w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag-300x218.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag-500x363.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag-276x200.png 276w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/canonical-tag-450x327.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 620px) 100vw, 620px\" /></p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Product pages with the variation in size and colors can be identified by canonical tags. Also, you can use pagination and show the canonical tag for category pages. </p>\n<h4>12.  Social sharing</h4>\n<p>We live in an age dominated by social media. No business can thrive without the help of social networks these days. </p>\n<blockquote><p>The social media can act as a replacement for word to mouth publicity.</p></blockquote>\n<p>When you integrate social sharing button, you enable your consumers to share their views on their social media accounts like Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest, etc. It can increase the visibility and referral traffic on your eCommerce website. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Magento 2 does not support social sharing but you can <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/share-whatsapp-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">install a module</a> for integrating this feature.  Magento web developers can add this feature to your existing eCommerce website with ease as well.  </p>\n<h4>13. Do Keyword research</h4>\n<p>Well, this is the most basic and yet one of the most effective SEO techniques to date.</p>\n<p>Actually, the main objective of SEO is to take your website’s position on the SERPs as high as possible for relevant keywords. You can use <a href=\"https://adwords.google.com/ko/KeywordPlanner/Home\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Google Keyword Planner</a>, <a href=\"https://www.semrush.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SEMRush</a>, or <a href=\"https://ahrefs.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Ahrefs</a> for researching keywords.</p>\n<p>In today’s competitive scenario, you should also keep an eye on the competitors’ online activities. Both SEMRush and Ahrefs enable you to peek into the competitor’s keywords and ranking. With the proper <a href=\"https://backlinko.com/keyword-research\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">keyword research</a>, you will better understand your customers and yield the highest return over investment (ROI).</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> It is better to find out primary and highest ranking keyword for your Magento store. You should aim for a single primary keyword or topic for each page. Usually, <b>lower volume keywords are easier to be ranked up</b> than higher volume keywords. Also, check the keywords used by your competitors for their popular products.</p>\n<h4>14. Keep URL short</h4>\n<p>URLs act as an address of your webpage. Therefore, it needs to be precise, keyword-rich, and short. Relevant and unique URLs can easily inform Google about the page’s theme and content. Remember, your <b>URL should contain a primary keyword</b>, but, there is no need for keyword stuffing.</p>\n<p>The search-friendly URL needs to contain at least one keyword. </p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44705\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Keep-URL-short.gif\" alt=\"Keep URL short\" width=\"650\" height=\"535\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44705\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">Image Source: Moz.com</p></div>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> You can exclude the category and sub-category to make your URL shorter.</p>\n<h4>15. Use Breadcrumbs</h4>\n<p>An eCommerce website is full of categories and sub-categories. The Breadcrumbs is very useful in such a website. It can make the navigation better for the user while simplifying the complicated structure of the website.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs.png\" alt=\"Breadcrumbs\" width=\"1319\" height=\"761\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44707\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs.png 1319w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-300x173.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-768x443.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-1024x591.png 1024w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-500x288.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-920x530.png 920w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-624x360.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-850x490.png 850w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-347x200.png 347w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/Breadcrumbs-450x260.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1319px) 100vw, 1319px\" /></p>\n<p>Breadcrumbs can show the navigation path of the product. It shows a better display in the search result, and the visitor can know the path. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Any Magento 2 store needs breadcrumbs to facilitate the visitor to search the product. </p>\n<h4>16. Write SEO-friendly Product Description</h4>\n<p>Content can make or break the reputation of your eCommerce business. When it comes to the online shop, the product page needs a rich piece of content. Such content can not only attract the visitors to become buyers but also help crawlers to judge the product. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Poorly written content can lead your webpage to the lower ranking.</p></blockquote>\n<p>When we say <b>SEO-friendly content</b>, it does not mean that you should write any superfluous words and use the heavy language. Simple but keyword-based content can work wonders for your webpage. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Here are a few tips to write <strong>SEO-based product description</strong>:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Write the description in detail to <strong>help people and crawlers</strong> understand your product</li>\n<li>It is better to <strong>set the H1, H2, and H3 tag</strong></li>\n<li>You should <strong>include the primary keyword</strong> in the heading</li>\n<li><strong>Other keywords</strong> should be included in the first and last part</li>\n<li><strong>Avoid keyword stuffing</strong> and keep the keyword density below 5 percent</li>\n<li>Try to <strong>put a link to related products</strong> in your description</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>17. Include Review and Rating</h4>\n<p>When it comes to the eCommerce website, the <strong>user-generated content can play a significant role</strong> in convincing other users. It can attract other people and <strong>improve the trustworthiness</strong> of your business. </p>\n<p>Rating and review matter a lot when people search for something and many online retailers offer it. Also, the chances of selection are high even of the product with a small description because of good reviews and rating. You can also <b>show the rating in rich snippets</b> for various products. </p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings.png\" alt=\"reviews-ratings\" width=\"796\" height=\"284\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44720\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings.png 796w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-300x107.png 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-768x274.png 768w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-500x178.png 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-624x223.png 624w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-350x125.png 350w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/reviews-ratings-450x161.png 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 796px) 100vw, 796px\" /></p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> Magento 2 enables you to show the rating and review as rich snippets. You can also include the Q&#038;A section. It can attract more users by giving them a chance to interact with your website. As a result, the bounce rate decreases and the CTR increases. Q&#038;A, reviews, and rating together empower your product to become a brand. </p>\n<h4>18. Keep Everything Simple</h4>\n<p>The eCommerce website should be simple enough to understand every product. Be it navigation or content, the visitor should readily find what they want on your store. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Don’t force your existing or prospective customers to read so much about your products.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Magento 2 is a robust platform that can include hundreds of thousands of products across different categories. But then, if you make the website complicated, you may lose the visitors due to an increasing competition. </p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> SEO requires to-the-point content and simple design. It is better to keep the end user in mind while developing a Magento 2 website for your business. If you think of Google bots, remember, they also hate complex words and irrelevant material on your website.</p>\n<h4>19. Write Title and Description Properly</h4>\n<p>Meta title and description are important from an SEO viewpoint. The <strong>meta title is responsible for the first impression</strong> for your webpages in the mind of visitors. It also impacts the <strong>CTR and conversion rate</strong>. Apart from including the main keyword or targeted keyword, the meta title needs to follow the following tips: </p>\n<ol>\n<li>It should be of <strong>50 to 60 characters</strong> long</li>\n<li>CTA (Call To Action) like <b>‘Buy Now’</b> can increase the <strong>CTR by 20%</strong></li>\n<li>You can <strong>show the USP of your product</strong> while writing a title for the product page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>After the title tag, the description comes. The meta description is different than the product description in two ways: One, <strong>it is written for the search engine</strong> and Two, <strong>it contains the keywords</strong> but it is shorter than the product description. It gives the additional information to the customers as one more reason to click!</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> It is difficult to write the right meta description for thousands of products. Here, the <b>third party Magento 2 extension</b> can assist you. It can <b>create meta info in bulk</b> and you can use variables like category and product feature to differentiate the meta description. </p>\n<p>Both <a href=\"https://support.google.com/webmasters/answer/35624?hl=en\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">meta title and description are important</a> from a search engine ranking perspective also. Therefore, they should be written precisely. You can take help of a <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento development company</a> for it.</p>\n<h4>20. Optimize Images</h4>\n<p>Many retailers fail to leverage the benefits of product images. It is because they have no idea of image optimization. You can <b>use the alt tag to optimize all your images</b>. Just fill the alt tag with your keyword and the crawlers will understand your image. </p>\n<blockquote><p>Alt tag helps your product to show in the image search and increases its visibility.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Another problem with an eCommerce website is a slow loading time. In a fast-growing domain like eCommerce and M-commerce, if your website takes a long to load, it is unacceptable. Therefore, you should optimize your images with their size reduced to <b>less than 100 kB</b>. It can decrease the PLT (Page Load Time) considerably.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> An eCommerce website contains a lot of images. All your product pages should contain at least one clear and catchy image to appeal visitors. It is even better if you can come up with images of the same products from different angles.</p>\n<p>That’s not all. As Google prefers <strong>rich media content</strong>, you should add the product videos for gaining traction and a higher ranking. People just love to watch how the product works and its benefits. Your product can also get an advantage of a video search. Just remember to put the product page link in your video’s description.  </p>\n<blockquote><p>If a picture is worth a thousand words, a product video could very well be worth a thousand sales.   -Neil Patel</p></blockquote>\n<h4>21. Add blog section</h4>\n<p>The <b>blog section</b> can serve many purposes. You can use the <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/product/magento-2-extensions/advanced-blog-magento-2/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">blog extension</a> for your Magento store. There is <b>no need to learn coding</b> or even a WordPress to start writing a blog for your Magento store. You can inform the visitors and customers about the new product launch, promotional offers, and trends with the help of a blog.</p>\n<p><b>Pro Tip:</b> It is better to update the blog section regularly. You can assign this task to the content marketing agency initially to grab the attention of visitors and customers. When you post blogs frequently, Google will also notice it, and give your blog a preference on the search pages.</p>\n<p><b>Conclusion</b><br />\nHere we gave you a comprehensive <b>Magento 2 SEO guide</b>. You should consult a leading <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento web development services provider</a> to get more idea of how you can boost web traffic for your existing or proposed Magento 2 store through search engine optimization techniques. </p>\n<p>At <strong>Solwin Infotech</strong>, we build a customer-friendly eCommerce store using the Magento platform. Our expert Magento developers can address your online business requirements effectively by integrating Magento 2 extensions and <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-themes/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 themes</a>. We have developed eCommerce websites for different products with over 60+ customized <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/magento-2-extensions/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Magento 2 extensions</a> and 15+ Magento extensions. </p>\n<p>Just <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">contact us</a> with your eCommerce concept and we will transform it into a full-fledged online shop with all user-friendly features and excellent appearance.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/\">20+ Most Effective Magneto 2 SEO Tips to Enhance Visibility of Your Online Store</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/seo/magneto-2-seo-tips/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"Artificial Intelligence – All Set to Transform the Internet (and WordPress)\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:89:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:98:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 30 Aug 2018 13:04:57 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:8:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Web Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:2;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"AI\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:3;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Artificial Intelligence\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Artificial Intelligence And Internet\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Artificial Intelligence And WordPress\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:6;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22:\"Web Development Future\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:7;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"WordPress Future\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:39:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/?p=44192\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:667:\"<p>AI (Artificial Intelligence) and machine learning have become a hot potato in the corporate world. As a futuristic technology, artificial intelligence is capable of bringing disruptive changes in our lives more than any other technologies. This is because AI touches every aspect of our life and can take part in every activity. Today, we witness </p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/\">Artificial Intelligence &#8211; All Set to Transform the Internet (and WordPress)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Sanjay Dabhoya\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14209:\"<p>AI (Artificial Intelligence) and machine learning have become a hot potato in the corporate world. As a futuristic technology, artificial intelligence is capable of bringing disruptive changes in our lives more than any other technologies. This is because AI touches every aspect of our life and can take part in every activity.</p>\n<p>Today, we witness that machines are getting better at learning and smarter at work. They can process, share, and analyze information like humans. As a result, machines have taken over many odd jobs that are otherwise performed by human beings.</p>\n<p>Self-driving cars, robotic limbs, and machine-operated elderly care instrument have no longer remained new to us. As the technology advances, machines have started interacted with us in a better and more efficient way than ever. Technological advancements and intelligent machines are all set to become an integral part of our daily life.</p>\n<p><strong>Both AI and ML (Machine Learning) can revolutionize the digital world.</strong> </p>\n<blockquote><p>In other words, AI has a significant role to play in using and interpreting the database and online processes based on data analysis.</p></blockquote>\n<p>Voice search is an epitome of what AI can do for us. From building websites to creating content, from serving the customers to responding to their queries- AI can serve many purposes on the Internet. Naturally, the CMS (Content Management System) is also no exception. As one of the most versatile and customizable platforms, <strong>WordPress has also started adopting the AI technology</strong>. A few WordPress plugins are now available that are driven by Artificial Intelligence.  It seems that the future versions of WordPress will be based on AI.</p>\n<p>Let us have a sneak peek of what AI brings for the Internet and WordPress. Just keep reading to know!</p>\n<h4>How AI will change the face of Web Design and Development?</h4>\n<p>Today’s websites are intuitive and innovative to offer a pleasant interactive experience to the visitors. Artificial Intelligence technology is integrated to facilitate human-like interaction in the business websites and eCommerce sites. Surprisingly, a few technology companies work on developing AI algorithms that can build the entire websites. The most important examples are <a href=\"https://www.wix.com/blog/2016/06/wix-artificial-design-intelligence/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Wix ADI</a> and <a href=\"https://firedrop.ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Firedrop</a>. It means that today, AI is partly used in the web design and development, but tomorrow, it can create the whole website. </p>\n<p class=\"text-center\"><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/YrERmaDZNl0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"autoplay; encrypted-media\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p class=\"text-center\"><strong>Source:</strong> wix.com</p>\n<p>An AI assistant takes the driver seat and helps users determine the type of websites. Then it can either take autonomous decisions on various design and development aspects like branding, content, and layout by itself. In the case of Firedrop, the AI assistant acts as a real-life web designer and enable the users to complete the development process with real-time suggestions.</p>\n<p><strong>In other words,</strong> AI works as a virtual assistant for the users and helps them create a unique website. What’s more, the AI technology has also entered into the field of graphic design as the users can utilize this technology for a few parts of web design. </p>\n<p>The AI-driven web development platforms are still in the nascent stage with limited capabilities. They can not build a robust website with desired features yet.  But we can certainly expect that AI will build complex enterprise websites in the future as we have taken the first step in this direction. </p>\n<p>Talking about the <strong>WordPress</strong>, we can predict that it would be the <strong>first platform and CMS</strong> on which the AI technology will handle the entire development process with ease. We have a strong reason behind this forecast: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/tags/ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">AI-powered plugins</a> are already available for WordPress. No other CMS has such ‘intelligent’ plugins to date. </p>\n<p>Also, we will see the WordPress themes powered by AI. These days, WordPress web development companies put their efforts into making the themes smarter than before. </p>\n<h4>Impact of Websites Built by AI</h4>\n<p>When it comes to user analysis and data process, <strong>AI is simply the best!</strong></p>\n<p>It can help web owners offer the best possible experience to the visitors by analyzing their intent. Just like personalized ads and search results, we will see the personalized website experience soon.</p>\n<p>In brief, the visitors will see the images and information as per their online behavior on the websites built by Artificial Intelligence. </p>\n<h4>How AI brings changes in E-Commerce Domain?</h4>\n<p>Thriving eCommerce domain offers a lot of scope to AI and machine learning.</p>\n<p><strong>As a customer-centric platform,</strong> eCommerce needs a continuous analysis of people’s shopping behavior and the user’s data to serve them in a better way. Amid growing competition, retailers count on AI and machine learning to stay ahead of the curve.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce.jpg\" alt=\"AI in E-Commerce\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44247\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce.jpg 612w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-150x150.jpg 150w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-300x300.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-500x500.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-370x370.jpg 370w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-75x75.jpg 75w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-165x165.jpg 165w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-200x200.jpg 200w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-450x450.jpg 450w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-in-E-Commerce-100x100.jpg 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></p>\n<blockquote><p>As per a Business Insider survey, almost 72 percent of retailers plan to invest in cognitive computing or machine learning by 2021.</p></blockquote>\n<p>It means that a lot of money will be invested in AI in the coming years.</p>\n<h4>Rich and Personalized Experience</h4>\n<p>The secret of success in the eCommerce business remains in understanding and serving the customers better with a more personalized experience.</p>\n<p>AI-based virtual shopping assistants can readily recommend similar and complementary products as per the customer’s shopping behavior.</p>\n<p><strong>How about offering compliments to your customers through machines?</strong></p>\n<p>AI and ML can do so for you. A survey says that personalization can increase the sales by two to three times. Do you know that WooCommerce, an eCommerce tool for WordPress, has an AI-powered, intelligent plugin? </p>\n<h4>Automated Services for Customers</h4>\n<p>The advent of chatbot and advancements of voice search have strengthened the AI’s presence in the digital space. </p>\n<p>Companies are working on providing <strong>virtual customer service agents</strong> to bring automation in the ordering and purchase process. Chatbots can play a significant role in this service.</p>\n<p>Apart from social platforms, chatbots or simply bots exist on WordPress as well. These tiny robots can learn from interactions and add answers to their libraries accordingly. The eCommerce retailers can provide the in-store experience to their customers online with the help of complex bots.</p>\n<p>Highly popular eCommerce platform <strong>Magento is ready to integrate AI</strong> and machine learning through the help of customized extensions. AI will enable the retailers to save both time and money by providing automated customer services in the near future.</p>\n<p>Isn’t it interesting that your customers will talk to your websites like they do to their home appliance? </p>\n<p>As AI technology gets matured and comes into the mainstream, the possibilities will also get bigger. We can also expect that the chatbots or robots will talk to people in different languages thanks to the language processing. </p>\n<h4>How Artificial Intelligence Will Influence Content Marketing?</h4>\n<p>Spell check, grammar-related and article-spinning software are a few of the most common examples of AI’s penetration in the domain of online writing.</p>\n<p>Today, we have applications to proofread and generate the titles. Days are not far when the robot will replace the professional writers.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_44223\" style=\"width: 601px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/grammarly.gif\" alt=\"grammarly\" width=\"591\" height=\"286\" class=\"size-full wp-image-44223\" /><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><strong>Source:</strong> Grammarly.com</p></div>\n<p><strong>What does it take to create compelling content?</strong></p>\n<p>Well, reading and compiling a plethora of information in a proper order with a human touch is the answer to this question. Now, machines can handle the extensive research work with ease. Initiating from making the writer’s job easier, AI looks ready to do their job!</p>\n<blockquote><p>Chances are bright that you will read the content written by a robot in the future.</p></blockquote>\n<p>However, machine learning can actually do a lot more than that. AI is getting increasingly better at understanding the context and intent behind written words. Therefore, it can now also correct style and grammar mistakes as well as make suggestions on how to improve your text further.</p>\n<p>If we think of such intelligent software in WordPress, immediately <a href=\"http://www.afterthedeadline.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">After the Deadline</a> comes in our mind. This language checker tool is included in the Jetpack plugin and takes care of three major writing aspects: spell check, style check, and grammar check.  </p>\n<p>There is no exaggeration in mentioning that <strong>AI will touch every aspect of the Internet</strong> like it does of our lives. Thanks to AI and machine learning, we would enter in the new age where machines will give us suggestions and enhance our convenience in almost all routine activities. </p>\n<h4>Impact on Employment</h4>\n<p>Every coin has two sides. Though AI is good at analyzing loads of data and bringing automation, it has limitations in taking creative decisions and finding subjective factors like emotional effect.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment.jpg\" alt=\"AI Impact On Employment\" width=\"612\" height=\"424\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-44252\" srcset=\"https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment.jpg 612w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment-300x208.jpg 300w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment-500x346.jpg 500w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment-289x200.jpg 289w, https://solwincdn-79e1.kxcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/AI-Impact-On-Employment-450x312.jpg 450w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 612px) 100vw, 612px\" /></p>\n<p>Creative professionals can take a sigh of relief because of such limitations but, entry-level workers may find it hard to keep their jobs when AI will be used in a full swing. We can put it like this: Repetitive and lower-level jobs can be lost to AI in the future. </p>\n<p><strong>Wrapping Up</strong></p>\n<p>Artificial Intelligence and Machine Learning are progressing slowly but steadily toward improving our lifestyle by adding comfort. </p>\n<blockquote><p>From ‘intelligent’ home appliances to ‘smart’ voice assistant, AI is ready to handle all sorts of complex activities.</p></blockquote>\n<p>In a way, it can bring drastic changes in our lives. As the technology is supported by the Internet, the web, eCommerce, and mobile app development domains will be impacted by AI. Days are not far when AI will build an entire business website.</p>\n<p>Altogether, leading CMS like WordPress and top-notch eCommerce platform like Magento will be impacted by AI in the future. It is interesting to see how AI will transform the web development and content creation in the future. </p>\n<p>We would love to hear your thoughts. Share your views about AI’s impact in the comment box below. </p>\n<p>At <strong>Solwin Infotech</strong>, we just love to integrate the cutting-edge technologies in our development processes. Thanks to the technological advancements and our dedicated developers’ focused approach, we have developed high-end <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/products/magento-2-extensions/\">Magento 2 extensions</a> and advanced <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/wordpress-plugins/\">WordPress plugins</a> to take your business to the next level. We are known for offering the best-in-class web and eCommerce development services in a cost-effective way to the global clientele. </p>\n<p>If you want to give your business a boost from thriving technology domain, just <a href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/contact-us/\">contact us</a> with your requirements and leave the development part on us!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/\">Artificial Intelligence &#8211; All Set to Transform the Internet (and WordPress)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.solwininfotech.com\">Solwin Infotech</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:94:\"https://www.solwininfotech.com/blog/wordpress/artificial-intelligence-internet-wordpress/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";