olor: #4c4c4c;\"><strong>MAIN INDUSTRIES:</strong> Coconut</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\"><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c;\"><strong>MAIN ATTRACTIONS:</strong> Surf, Beach, Windmills, Delicacies</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\"><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c;\"><strong>HISTORICAL FIGURES:</strong> Marcoses, Aglipay Church</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"font_9\"><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c;\"><strong>MAJOR TRANSPORTS:</strong> PhilTranco, Farinas, DLTB, PAL</span></p>\r[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_image src=\"http://207.180.199.176/~silippin/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/pbnad.jpg\" align=\"center\" _builder_version=\"3.17.6\" background_color=\"#5170ff\" custom_margin=\"||\" custom_padding=\"40px||40px\" background__hover_enabled=\"on\"]\r[/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" custom_padding=\"0|0px|38px|0px|false|false\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"3.0.48\" background_size=\"initial\" background_position=\"top_left\" background_repeat=\"repeat\" custom_padding=\"24px|0px|27px|0px|false|false\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb url=\"#\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%154%%\" icon_color=\"#5170ff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#5170ff\" _builder_version=\"3.17.6\" link_option_url=\"#\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SilipKainan</strong></h3>[/et_pb_blurb][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_4\" _builder_version=\"3.0.47\" parallax=\"off\" parallax_method=\"on\"][et_pb_blurb url=\"#\" use_icon=\"on\" font_icon=\"%%122%%\" icon_color=\"#5170ff\" use_circle=\"on\" circle_color=\"#ffffff\" use_circle_border=\"on\" circle_border_color=\"#5170ff\" _builder_version=\"3.17.6\" link_option_url=\"#\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>SilipPasyalan</strong></